{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>有一个方格矩阵，矩阵边界在无穷远处。我们做如下假设：<p><p>a、每走一步时，只能从当前方格移动一格，走到某个相邻的方格上；<p><p>b、走过的格子立即塌陷无法再走第二次；<p><p>c、只能向北、东、西三个方向走；<p><p>请问：如果允许在方格矩阵上走n步，共有多少种不同的方案。2种走法只要有一步不一样，即被认为是不同的方案。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"踩方格 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>计算出的方案数量。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>允许在方格上行走的步数n(n≤20)。<p>","examples":"<input>2\n</input><output>7\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1196","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}